        <p data-role="text">Each night, the five women still in the group leave the restau&#xAD;rant in a few cars, with the man tak&#xAD;ing a ride in one of the ve&#xAD;hi&#xAD;cles to his flat in the west&#xAD;ern part of Sin&#xAD;ga&#xAD;pore.</p>
    </div>

